5ad4e699-da35-4dc8-87e0-cfc85908ecba.do_description: To make the output, you have to...start at the colored square and add a same colored square to make a x shape for the whole square
5ad4e699-da35-4dc8-87e0-cfc85908ecba.grid_description: The output grid size...is the same as the input
5ad4e699-da35-4dc8-87e0-cfc85908ecba.see_description: In the input, you should see...one colored square on a black background

9402efe1-0908-40d2-b678-db2ffdc787c8.do_description: To make the output, you have to...add squares on each of the four corners of the square all the way to the edge in the same color, should look like a sword
9402efe1-0908-40d2-b678-db2ffdc787c8.grid_description: The output grid size...same as input
9402efe1-0908-40d2-b678-db2ffdc787c8.see_description: In the input, you should see...one colored square

bd009b25-490c-48ce-9742-41949b7e2c8c.do_description: To make the output, you have to...add squares of the same color as the original square such that each added square extends diagonally in 4 directions from each corner of the original square until each line extending from the original square reaches a side or a corner of the grid. The diagonal lines will form an X pattern that may have one of more long arms or legs
bd009b25-490c-48ce-9742-41949b7e2c8c.grid_description: The output grid size...is the same as the input
bd009b25-490c-48ce-9742-41949b7e2c8c.see_description: In the input, you should see...one colored square on a black background

cf3b8443-1b33-4d03-80dd-b010b8c7e2e3.do_description: To make the output, you have to...add the same colored box on all four corners to form an X. Continue out from those boxes in a straight line to form a cross or t shape.
cf3b8443-1b33-4d03-80dd-b010b8c7e2e3.grid_description: The output grid size...same as input
cf3b8443-1b33-4d03-80dd-b010b8c7e2e3.see_description: In the input, you should see...one colored box
